# Nanobridge Overview

OpenAI- and Anthropic-compatible API gateway for developers. Routes to DeepSeek, GLM, MiniMax, and other models on Tencent Hunyuan backends.

---

## Why Nanobridge

- **OpenAI compatible**: change `base_url` and `model` in existing apps
- **Multi-region gateways**: Germany, Singapore, United States—one API key
- **Coding workloads**: retry, routing, and agent toolchains
- **Flexible billing**: top up in the console; crypto and other payment options (see console)
- **No credit-card barrier**: useful when international cards are declined

---

## Gateway vs console

| Purpose | Host |
|---------|------|
| Sign-up, keys, billing, docs | `https://platform.nanobridge.net` |
| **Inference API** | `https://api.nanobridge.net` (and `api-sg`, `api-us`) |

Never use `platform.nanobridge.net` as the Chat Completions base URL.

---

## Pricing

Rates are shown in the console under **Pricing / model catalog** and may change with upstream pricing:

https://platform.nanobridge.net

Token usage and credit deductions in docs and billing follow the console as the source of truth.

---

## Quick start (Python)

```python
from openai import OpenAI

client = OpenAI(
    api_key="YOUR_NANOBRIDGE_KEY",
    base_url="https://api.nanobridge.net/v1",
)

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="deepseek-v4-flash",
    messages=[{"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"}],
)
print(response.choices[0].message.content)
```

